### Audit
- Reviewed enterprise milestone priorities and current operational memory.
- Identified a security/reliability gap in `PATCH /api/admin/users`:
- no self-role-change guard
- no last-admin demotion protection
- limited role-change audit detail

### Plan
- Harden admin role mutation path first (security/reliability priority).
- Keep change additive and backward-compatible.
- Verify with build; if blocked, provide exact unblock commands.

### Implement
Hardened `src/app/api/admin/users/route.ts`:
- Enforced actor user id presence before mutation flow.
- Blocked self-role updates (`You cannot change your own role`).
- Added explicit target-user existence check.
- Added deterministic no-op response when role is unchanged.
- Prevented demotion of the last remaining `ADMIN`.
- Expanded audit detail to include `previousRole` + `newRole`.

